            <% } %>
        </li>
    </ul>
</nav>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>

    <main class="container-fluid text-white">
        <section id="MainBody" class="py-5">
            <h2 id="wup" class="section-title">So, what's up?</h2>
            
            <div class="row justify-content-center mb-5">
                <div class="col-md-10">
                    <div class="info-card">
                        <div class="row">
                            <div class="col-md-4 text-center mb-4">
                                <img src="https://images.theconversation.com/files/377023/original/file-20210104-23-1gss1v1.jpg?ixlib=rb-4.1.0&rect=4%2C2%2C994%2C661&q=20&auto=format&w=320&fit=clip&dpr=2&usm=12&cs=strip"
                                    alt="Sea Pollution" class="custom-img" data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#problemModal">
                                <div class="mt-3">
                                    <button class="btn btn-primary" data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#problemModal">Research Sources & Further Reading</button>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-md-8">
                                <h3 class="mb-3">The Ocean Pollution Crisis</h3>
                                <p>Our oceans face an unprecedented threat from human activities. Every year, millions of tons of plastic waste enter marine ecosystems, while chemical pollutants and agricultural runoff create dead zones where marine life cannot survive.</p>
                                
                                <h5 class="mt-4">Primary Pollution Sources</h5>
                                <div class="row">
                                    <div class="col-md-6">
                                        <ul>
                                            <li><strong>Plastic Pollution:</strong> 8 million tons enter oceans annually, harming over 700 species</li>
                                            <li><strong>Chemical Contaminants:</strong> Industrial waste, pesticides, and heavy metals</li>
                                            <li><strong>Nutrient Pollution:</strong> Agricultural runoff causing algal blooms and dead zones</li>
                                            <li><strong>Oil Spills:</strong> Major accidents and routine shipping operations</li>
                                        </ul>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="col-md-6">
                                        <h5>Scientific Publications</h5>
                                        <p>For deeper research, consult these key scientific journals:</p>
                                        <ul>
                                            <li>Marine Pollution Bulletin</li>
                                            <li>Environmental Science & Technology</li>
                                            <li>Nature Communications - Environmental Studies</li>
                                            <li>Science of The Total Environment</li>
                                        </ul>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                
                                <div class="row mt-4">
                                    <div class="col-md-6">
                                        <h5>Immediate Threats</h5>
                                        <ul>
                                            <li>Plastic pollution affecting over 700 species</li>
                                            <li>Chemical contamination from industrial waste</li>
                                            <li>Coral reef bleaching and destruction</li>
                                            <li>Overfishing disrupting food chains</li>
                                        </ul>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="col-md-6">
                                        <h5>Long-term Impacts</h5>
                                        <ul>
                                            <li>Biodiversity loss and ecosystem collapse</li>
                                            <li>Threats to global food security</li>
                                            <li>Economic damage to coastal communities</li>
                                            <li>Climate regulation disruption</li>
                                        </ul>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                
                                <p class="mt-3">The time for action is now. Understanding the scale and complexity of marine pollution is the first step toward developing effective solutions.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="row justify-content-center mb-5">
                <div class="col-md-10">
                    <h3 class="text-center mb-4">Critical Ocean Statistics</h3>
                    <div class="row text-center">
                        <div class="col-md-3 mb-4">
                            <div class="stat-card">
                                <div class="stat-number">8M</div>
                                <div class="stat-label">Tons of plastic enter oceans yearly</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-3 mb-4">
                            <div class="stat-card">
                                <div class="stat-number">700</div>
                                <div class="stat-label">Marine species affected by plastic</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-3 mb-4">
                            <div class="stat-card">
                                <div class="stat-number">500</div>
                                <div class="stat-label">Dead zones where marine life can't survive</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-3 mb-4">
                            <div class="stat-card">
                                <div class="stat-number">80%</div>
                                <div class="stat-label">Of pollution comes from land sources</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="row justify-content-center mb-5">
                <div class="col-md-10">
                    <div class="row justify-content-center">
                        <div class="col-md-4 text-center mb-4">
                            <img class="custom-img img-rotate1" src="https://cleanwater.org/sites/default/files/images/actions/RI_plastic%20on%20beach_canva.jpg"
                                alt="Plastic on beach" data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#plasticModal">
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-4 text-center mb-4">
                            <img class="custom-img img-rotate2" src="https://www.greenpeace.org/static/planet4-international-stateless/2020/09/5a4f7d68-gp1su9nb-1024x576.jpg"
                                alt="Ocean pollution" data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#pollutionModal">
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-4 text-center mb-4">
                            <img class="custom-img img-rotate3" src="https://www.reuters.com/resizer/v2/https%3A%2F%2Farchive-images.prod.global.a201836.reutersmedia.net%2F2015%2F02%2F13%2FLYNXMPEB1C006.JPG?auth=0f29dc60dbdb8dee529157047c46460e768cd35341ba1d6e202c4d539422c3e4&width=1080&quality=80"
                                alt="Oil spill" data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#oilModal">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
        
        <section id="History" class="py-5">
            <h2 class="section-title">Problem's History</h2>
            
            <div class="row justify-content-center mb-5">
                <div class="col-md-10">
                    <div class="info-card">
                        <div class="row">
                            <div class="col-md-7">
                                <h3 class="mb-3">Key Historical Moments</h3>
                                
                                <div class="timeline-highlights">
                                    <div class="timeline-item">
                                        <div class="timeline-date">1962</div>
                                        <div class="timeline-content">
                                            <h6>Silent Spring Published</h6>
                                            <p>Rachel Carson's groundbreaking book raises public awareness about pesticide impacts, sparking modern environmental movement.</p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    
                                    <div class="timeline-item">
                                        <div class="timeline-date">1967</div>
                                        <div class="timeline-content">
                                            <h6>Torrey Canyon Oil Spill</h6>
                                            <p>First major tanker disaster spills 120,000 tons of oil off UK coast, highlighting vulnerability of marine ecosystems.</p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    
                                    <div class="timeline-item">
                                        <div class="timeline-date">1972</div>
                                        <div class="timeline-content">
                                            <h6>Clean Water Act Passed</h6>
                                            <p>Landmark US legislation regulates pollutant discharges and ocean dumping, setting precedent for global environmental policy.</p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    
                                    <div class="timeline-item">
                                        <div class="timeline-date">1997</div>
                                        <div class="timeline-content">
                                            <h6>Great Pacific Garbage Patch Discovered</h6>
                                            <p>Oceanographer Charles Moore discovers massive plastic accumulation zone in North Pacific, drawing global attention to plastic pollution.</p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            
                            <div class="col-md-5">
                                <div class="text-center">
                                    <iframe width="100%" height="200" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/uRE_DndxwaA?si=NVRL-L6HIuixjy7Z" 
                                    title="YouTube video player" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" 
                                    referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen>
                                    </iframe>
                                    <div class="mt-3">
                                        <small class="text-muted">Watch: The history of ocean pollution and conservation efforts</small>
                                    </div>
                                    <button class="btn btn-primary mt-3" data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#historyModal">Explore Full Historical Timeline</button>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="row justify-content-center">
                <div class="col-md-10">
                    <div class="info-card">
                        <div class="row">
                            <div class="col-md-6">
                                <h5>Current Global Initiatives</h5>
                                <ul>
                                    <li>UN Sustainable Development Goal 14: Life Below Water</li>
                                    <li>Paris Agreement climate commitments</li>
                                    <li>Global plastic reduction treaties</li>
                                    <li>Marine protected area expansion</li>
                                    <li>Corporate sustainability pledges</li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-md-6">
                                <h5>Technological Innovations</h5>
                                <ul>
                                    <li>Ocean cleanup systems and barriers</li>
                                    <li>Biodegradable plastic alternatives</li>
                                    <li>Satellite monitoring of pollution</li>
                                    <li>AI-powered waste sorting</li>
                                    <li>Circular economy models</li>
                                </ul>
                                
                                <p>The challenge has evolved from visible cleanup to systemic change in how we produce and consume, requiring global cooperation and innovative solutions.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
        
        <section id="GetInspired" class="py-5">
            <h2 class="section-title">Get Inspired</h2>
            
            <div class="row justify-content-center mb-5">
                <div class="col-md-8 text-center">
                    <div class="quote-container bg-light text-dark p-4 rounded shadow">
                        <blockquote class="blockquote mb-0">
                            <p class="quote-text fs-4 fst-italic">"<%= quote.text %>"</p>
                            <footer class="blockquote-footer mt-3 fs-5">
                                <cite title="Source Title"><%= quote.author %></cite>
                            </footer>
                        </blockquote>
                    </div>
                    <p class="text-muted mt-3">Daily inspiration to protect our oceans</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
        
        <section id="Consequences" class="py-5">
            <h2 class="section-title">Consequences</h2>
            
            <div class="row justify-content-center mb-5">
                <div class="col-md-10">
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
                            <div class="consequence-box h-100" data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#ecosystemModal">
                                <h4>Ecosystem Destruction</h4>
                                <p class="consequence-text">Pollution introduces harmful chemicals and plastics that kill marine life through ingestion and entanglement. It destroys critical habitats like coral reefs and creates oxygen-depleted dead zones where no life can survive.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
                            <div class="consequence-box h-100" data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#healthModal">
                                <h4>Human Health Impact</h4>
                                <p class="consequence-text">Toxins like mercury and microplastics accumulate in seafood, posing serious health risks. Pollution also devastates fishing industries and tourism, burdening communities with massive cleanup costs and economic losses.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
                            <div class="consequence-box h-100" data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#climateModal">
                                <h4>Climate Disruption</h4>
                                <p class="consequence-text">Ocean acidification from absorbed CO2 compromises the ocean's ability to regulate climate. This weakens Earth's natural defenses against climate change and disrupts vital planetary systems that support all life.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="row justify-content-center">
                <div class="col-md-6 text-center">
                    <iframe class="video" width="100%" height="350" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/Yomf5pBN8dY?si=hzee2Cq8IcZ0LIOX" title="YouTube video player" 
                        frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" 
                        allowfullscreen>
                    </iframe>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

    <!-- User Modal -->
    <div class="modal fade" id="userModal" tabindex="-1" aria-labelledby="userModalLabel" aria-hidden="true">
        <div class="modal-dialog">
            <div class="modal-content">
                <div class="modal-header">
                    <h5 class="modal-title" id="userModalLabel">User Profile</h5>
                    <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"></button>
                </div>
                <div class="modal-body">
                    <% if (user) { %>
                        <div class="text-center mb-3">
                            <img src="<%= user.photos[0].value %>" alt="User" class="rounded-circle" width="80" height="80">
                        </div>
                        <p><strong>Name:</strong> <%= user.displayName %></p>
                        <p><strong>Email:</strong> <%= user.emails[0].value %></p>
                        <p><strong>Member since:</strong> <%= new Date().toLocaleDateString() %></p>
                    <% } else { %>
                        <div class="text-center">
                            <p>Please log in to view your profile</p>
                            <a href="/auth/google" class="btn btn-primary">Login with Google</a>
                        </div>
                    <% } %>
                </div>
                <div class="modal-footer">
                    <% if (user) { %>
                        <a href="/logout" class="btn btn-warning">Logout</a>
                    <% } %>
                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" data-bs-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Problem Modal -->
    <div class="modal fade" id="problemModal" tabindex="-1" aria-labelledby="problemModalLabel" aria-hidden="true">
        <div class="modal-dialog modal-lg">
            <div class="modal-content">
                <div class="modal-header">
                    <h5 class="modal-title" id="problemModalLabel">Research Sources & Further Reading</h5>
                    <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"></button>
                </div>
                <div class="modal-body">
                    <div class="alert alert-info">
                        <strong>Note:</strong> Without immediate action, these pollutants will cause irreversible damage to marine ecosystems and human livelihoods. Current research shows we have a narrow window to implement effective solutions.
                    </div>
                    
                    <h6>Research & Data Sources</h6>
                    <ul>
                        <li><a href="https://www.un.org/sustainabledevelopment/oceans/" target="_blank">UN Sustainable Development Goals - Oceans</a></li>
                        <li><a href="https://www.iucn.org/resources/issues-brief/marine-plastic-pollution" target="_blank">IUCN Marine Plastic Pollution Brief</a></li>
                        <li><a href="https://oceanconservancy.org/trash-free-seas/" target="_blank">Ocean Conservancy Research</a></li>
                        <li><a href="https://www.nationalgeographic.com/environment/article/plastic-pollution" target="_blank">National Geographic Plastic Coverage</a></li>
                        <li><a href="https://www.noaa.gov/education/resource-collections/ocean-coasts/ocean-pollution" target="_blank">NOAA Ocean Pollution Education</a></li>
                    </ul>
                    
                    <h6 class="mt-4">Additional Information</h6>
                    <p>Marine pollution encompasses a wide range of contaminants entering ocean environments, with devastating consequences for ecosystems and human communities worldwide. The complexity of this issue requires multidisciplinary approaches combining science, policy, and community engagement.</p>
                    
                    <p>Recent studies show that microplastics have been found in the most remote marine environments, including deep-sea trenches and Arctic ice, demonstrating the pervasive nature of this pollution. Additionally, new research continues to reveal the long-term impacts of chemical pollutants on marine life and human health through the food chain.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="modal-footer">
                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" data-bs-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- History Modal -->
    <div class="modal fade" id="historyModal" tabindex="-1" aria-labelledby="historyModalLabel" aria-hidden="true">
        <div class="modal-dialog modal-lg">
            <div class="modal-content">
                <div class="modal-header">
                    <h5 class="modal-title" id="historyModalLabel">Marine Pollution Historical Timeline</h5>
                    <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"></button>
                </div>
                <div class="modal-body">
                    <div class="timeline">
                        <div class="timeline-item">
                            <div class="timeline-date">Pre-Industrial Era</div>
                            <div class="timeline-content">
                                <h6>Limited Environmental Impact</h6>
                                <p>Oceans viewed as infinite dumping grounds with minimal regulation. Pollution primarily from limited shipping and coastal settlements.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="timeline-item">
                            <div class="timeline-date">1950s</div>
                            <div class="timeline-content">
                                <h6>Plastic Revolution Begins</h6>
                                <p>Mass production of plastics transforms consumer goods. Chemical industry expands dramatically with new synthetic compounds.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="timeline-item">
                            <div class="timeline-date">1962</div>
                            <div class="timeline-content">
                                <h6>Silent Spring Published</h6>
                                <p>Rachel Carson's groundbreaking book raises public awareness about pesticide impacts, sparking modern environmental movement.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="timeline-item">
                            <div class="timeline-date">1967</div>
                            <div class="timeline-content">
                                <h6>Torrey Canyon Oil Spill</h6>
                                <p>First major tanker disaster spills 120,000 tons of oil off UK coast, highlighting vulnerability of marine ecosystems.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="timeline-item">
                            <div class="timeline-date">1972</div>
                            <div class="timeline-content">
                                <h6>Clean Water Act & Marine Protection</h6>
                                <p>Landmark US legislation regulates pollutant discharges and ocean dumping, setting precedent for global environmental policy.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="timeline-item">
                            <div class="timeline-date">1980s-1990s</div>
                            <div class="timeline-content">
                                <h6>Environmental Awareness Grows</h6>
                                <p>Discovery of ozone hole (1985) and increasing evidence of climate change. Exxon Valdez disaster (1989) further highlights oil spill risks.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="timeline-item">
                            <div class="timeline-date">1997</div>
                            <div class="timeline-content">
                                <h6>Great Pacific Garbage Patch Discovered</h6>
                                <p>Oceanographer Charles Moore discovers massive plastic accumulation zone in North Pacific, drawing global attention to plastic pollution.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="timeline-item">
                            <div class="timeline-date">2000s-Present</div>
                            <div class="timeline-content">
                                <h6>Microplastic Era & Global Response</h6>
                                <p>Microplastic contamination discovered globally. Ocean acidification recognized as major threat. International agreements and cleanup technologies emerge.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="mt-4">
                        <h6>Further Reading & Historical Resources</h6>
                        <ul>
                            <li><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=a35ffqcF_ZA" target="_blank">Ocean Pollution - United Nations Development Programme (UNDP)</a></li>
                            <li><a href="https://www.epa.gov/history" target="_blank">EPA History - Environmental Protection Agency</a></li>
                            <li><a href="https://www.unep.org/explore-topics/oceans-seas" target="_blank">UN Environment Programme - Oceans</a></li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="modal-footer">
                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" data-bs-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Ecosystem Modal -->
    <div class="modal fade" id="ecosystemModal" tabindex="-1" aria-labelledby="ecosystemModalLabel" aria-hidden="true">
        <div class="modal-dialog">
            <div class="modal-content">
                <div class="modal-header">
                    <h5 class="modal-title" id="ecosystemModalLabel">Ecosystem Impact</h5>
                    <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"></button>
                </div>
                <div class="modal-body">
                    <p>Marine pollution devastates ecosystems through multiple pathways:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Coral reef bleaching and destruction</li>
                        <li>Marine animal entanglement and ingestion of plastics</li>
                        <li>Formation of oxygen-depleted dead zones</li>
                        <li>Disruption of reproductive cycles</li>
                        <li>Loss of biodiversity and habitat destruction</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="modal-footer">
                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" data-bs-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha1/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>